fulltitle: Church Committee: NSA Surveillance Affecting Americans (B3.S10)
title: Church Committee: NSA Surveillance Affecting Americans (B3.S10)
description:
'Our Hidden History' Audiobooks: https://sellfy.com/OurHiddenHistory More Church Committee Reports: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLBINnEpNu5u5DDKZr3zRDb9v_Q2pV55dA ---- This is an audio recording of the ninth section of the third book of the Church Committee Final Report -- "Supplementary Detailed Staff Reports on Intelligence Activities and the Rights of Americans, NATIONAL SECURITY AGENCY SURVEILLANCE AFFECTING AMERICANS". 

The Church Committee, officially known as the United States Senate Select Committee to Study Governmental Operations with Respect to Intelligence Activities, was a committee charged with investigating abuses by the intelligence agencies of the United States. This section of the report deals with Covert Actions undertaken by the US Government. 

The full book can be found at the AARC Online Library: 
http://www.aarclibrary.org/publib/church/reports/book3/contents.htm

This audio book was narrated by Chris Abernathy (https://www.fiverr.com/provoman) and produced by D. Giglio for 'Our Hidden History'.

For more related content, please visit: https://archive.org/details/@altviewstv-fanclub
